302
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,320
Dear,

303
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,440
thank you.

304
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,519
Let me get you some ointment.

305
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:51,840
