324
00:14:04,580 --> 00:14:08,400
♪Oh, men, those smarty-pants♪

325
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,880
♪The backfire of your overflowing charm♪

326
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:15,520
♪Has no mercy♪

327
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:19,240
♪May your life be barren♪

328
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:21,480
♪May you tread on a thorny path alone♪

329
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:22,960
♪May you vanish into thin air♪

330
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,760
♪Lies will adorn your tombstone♪

331
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:27,200
♪Release me from this hatred♪

332
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:29,280
♪Free me from this excruciating cage♪

333
00:14:29,580 --> 00:14:31,040
♪Let me go to light♪

334
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:33,560
♪Let's never meet again♪

335
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:35,120
♪When I use your words♪

336
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,040
