337
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:38,320
♪You blame me for being cruel♪

338
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:41,280
♪Life is ironic♪

339
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:42,920
♪I want your end♪

340
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:44,000
♪To be lonely♪

